#

Spicy Garlic Butter Shrimp Pasta with Zucchini Noodles

$15.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-Carb

Tags:

SeafoodPastaHealthySpicy

Description

Succulent shrimp sautéed in a rich garlic butter sauce, served over spiralized zucchini for a light yet indulgent meal.

Ingredients

  • Shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 pound
  • Zucchini (spiralized): 2 medium
  • Butter: 4 tablespoons
  • Garlic (minced): 5 cloves
  • Red pepper flakes: 1 teaspoon
  • Lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • Parsley (fresh, chopped): 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
